text: Partido Demócrata Cristiano may refer to: * Partido Demócrata Cristiano (Argentina), a political party in Argentina * Partido Demócrata Cristiano (Bolivia), a political party in Bolivia * Partido Demócrata Cristiano de Chile, a political party in Chile * Partido Demócrata Cristiano (El Salvador), a political party in El Salvador * Partido Demócrata Cristiano, former name of the People's Party in Panama * Partido Demócrata Cristiano (Paraguay), a political party in Paraguay * Christian Democrat Party (Peru) * Partido Demócrata Cristiano del Uruguay, a political party in Uruguay ==See also== *Christian Democratic Party (disambiguation)
title: Partido Demócrata Cristiano
